  * Fixed audio crackling in Ubuntu 16.04
  * Changed audio buffer settings to fix buffer underruns
  * Fixed freeze when opening OpenScribe with a command line argument
  * Fixed freeze when opening OpenScribe from the Open With dialog in a file browser
  * Fixed changelog window to have proper word wrapping

