openscribe (1.1-0ubuntu2~trusty1) trusty; urgency=low

  * Fixed dependency issue that prevented OpenScribe from being installed on systems with a newer version of udev
  * Changed default audio chunk size from 15ms to 25ms to prevent audio crackling on slower systems
  * Changed error message when unable to load an audio file to be more informative

